      <th>1</th>
      <td>Source</td>
      <td>• SUCCESS: The replication was successful.\n• PENDING: The object hasn’t been replicated yet.\n• FAILURE: The replication failed with a permanent failure. A user\nmust resolve the error.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>2</th>
